HEADWORD: Retailer
<hw>Re*tail"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who retails
anything; <as>as, a <ex>retailer</ex> of merchandise; a
<ex>retailer</ex> of gossip</as>; -- used also of businesses, including
large corporations; <as>as, <org>Sears, Roebuck</org> is one the the
country's largest <ex>retailers</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Retailment</ent>⟦br⟧
